Fall into my arms

39:32.760 --> 39:37.060
Fall into my arms

39:37.110 --> 39:41.456
Fall into my arms

39:41.500 --> 39:45.800
Fall into my arms

39:45.860 --> 39:50.240
Fall into my arms

39:50.300 --> 39:54.464
Go on, take your time,
take a breath

39:54.520 --> 39:58.035
When you've had
to take it back

39:58.090 --> 40:03.039
Oh, baby,
know you can take it back

40:03.090 --> 40:07.652
It's never gonna
stay this way

40:09.450 --> 40:11.964
When the tears
that you cried

40:12.010 --> 40:16.014
Don't say
What you feel inside

40:16.060 --> 40:18.927
I'll be here,
but you decide

40:18.980 --> 40:20.936
Yeah, you decide

40:20.980 --> 40:25.155
When you wanna
fall into my arms

40:25.200 --> 40:29.409
- Fall into my arms
- 'Cause I know that
you're hurting

40:29.470 --> 40:33.895
- Fall into my arms
_- I know that
it's a sure thing

40:33.950 --> 40:37.943
- Fall into my arms
